name: Bone Collector
description: Bone Collector is a hybrid weed strain made from a genetic cross between Larry OG and Grandaddy Purple. This strain is 40% sativa and 60% indica. Bone Collector is 22% THC, making this strain an ideal choice for experienced cannabis consumers. Bred by Phat Panda, the average price of Bone Collector typically ranges from $10-$15 per gram.
